        {
            "id": "https://klausopaul.github.io/mytoolbox/great.html",
            "url": "https://klausopaul.github.io/mytoolbox/great.html",
            "title": "G.R.E.A.T.",
            "summary": "Here's another acronym to remember what makes for a great meeting. ",
            "content_html": "<p>Here's another acronym to remember what makes for a <em>great</em> meeting.</p>\n<table style=\"border-collapse: collapse; width: 104.486%; height: 100%; border-style: none;\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"2px\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 6.94668%;\">G</td>\n<td style=\"width: 27.6743%;\">GOAL</td>\n<td style=\"width: 67.0337%;\">Make decisions, mobilize people</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 6.94668%;\">R</td>\n<td style=\"width: 27.6743%;\">ROLES</td>\n<td style=\"width: 67.0337%;\">Who will be the time, the scriber, the devil's advocate</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 6.94668%;\">E</td>\n<td style=\"width: 27.6743%;\">EXPECTED OUTCOME</td>\n<td style=\"width: 67.0337%;\"> </td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 6.94668%;\">A</td>\n<td style=\"width: 27.6743%;\">AGENDA</td>\n<td style=\"width: 67.0337%;\">How to get (steps) to the outcome</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 6.94668%;\">T</td>\n<td style=\"width: 27.6743%;\">TIME</td>\n<td style=\"width: 67.0337%;\">Realistic time to discus and achieve outcome</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p> </p>",
